title: Gwen Stefani Calls In to Thank Dave For Playing Slow Clap!
description: We talked to our boss Rich about getting Gwen Stefani on the show since Dave keeps claiming that "Slow Clap" will be the Song of the Summer and plays it all the time and Rich set it up so we chat with her and she thanks Dave!
